    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_777-962",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "777-962",
      "markText": "道者，令民与上同意也，故可以与之死，可以与之生，而不畏危。",
      "totalCount": 1139,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=777&rangeEnd=962",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=777&rangeEnd=962"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_757-777",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "757-777",
      "markText": "一曰道，二曰天，三曰地，四曰将，五曰法。",
      "totalCount": 1080,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=777",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=777"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_1673-1716",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1673-1716",
      "markText": "主孰有道？将孰有能？天地孰得？法令孰行？兵众孰强？士卒孰练？赏罚孰明？吾以此知胜负矣。",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1716",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1716"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_9356-9380",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "9356-9380",
      "markText": "可是苻坚已经下了灭晋的决心，什么意见也听不进去。",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9356&rangeEnd=9380",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9356&rangeEnd=9380"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_5463-5489",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "5463-5489",
      "markText": "用兵打仗讲究诡谲之术，要运用多种方法来欺骗麻痹敌人。",
      "totalCount": 935,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5463&rangeEnd=5489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5463&rangeEnd=5489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_4409-4646",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4409-4646",
      "markText": "夫未战而庙算胜者，得算多也；未战而庙算不胜者，得算少也。多算胜，少算不胜，而况于无算乎？吾以此观之，胜负见矣。",
      "totalCount": 880,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4409&rangeEnd=4646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4409&rangeEnd=4646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_24_6897-6969",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "6897-6969",
      "markText": "“形”指的是运动的物质，“势”则指物质的运动，可以说，“形”是基础，“势”则是结果，“形”有展示显露的端倪，而“势”则是现象之下隐藏的必然趋向。",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6897&rangeEnd=6969",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6897&rangeEnd=6969"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_23_5353-5410",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5353-5410",
      "markText": "打胜仗的军队总是先取得必胜的条件，然后才寻找机会与敌人交战；打败仗的军队总是先与敌人交战，然后在战争中企图侥幸取胜",
      "totalCount": 855,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5353&rangeEnd=5410",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5353&rangeEnd=5410"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_27_4585-4665",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "4585-4665",
      "markText": "一般用兵打仗的原则是，不要把希望寄托在敌人不来进犯上，而是要依靠自己做好充分的准备，严阵以待；不要把希望寄托在敌人不会攻击上，而是要依靠自己的力量，将防守做好。",
      "totalCount": 816,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4585&rangeEnd=4665",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4585&rangeEnd=4665"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_21_4654-4662",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "4654-4662",
      "markText": "故兵贵胜，不贵久",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4654&rangeEnd=4662",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4654&rangeEnd=4662"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_4802-4835",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4802-4835",
      "markText": "战争要综合考虑五个方面的真实情况，即政治、天时、地利、将帅、法制。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4802&rangeEnd=4835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4802&rangeEnd=4835"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_7195-7246",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "7195-7246",
      "markText": "我临敌先示之以不能，以骄其志；我再示之以可乘之利，以贪其心。待其急切出击而空其守，我趁机发起突然袭击。",
      "totalCount": 715,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=7195&rangeEnd=7246",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=7195&rangeEnd=7246"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_6043-6093",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "6043-6093",
      "markText": "成功的关键在于事先的谋划分析，能够依据客观实际情况制定出切实可行的战略战术。这就是孙子所说的“计”。",
      "totalCount": 708,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=6043&rangeEnd=6093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=6043&rangeEnd=6093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "838856_20_10643-10708",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "10643-10708",
      "markText": "站在寿阳城上的苻坚看到晋军勇猛顽强，攻势强劲，误以为晋军部队人数极多，甚至把淝水东面八公山上的草木都误认为是晋兵，也开始害怕起来。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10643&rangeEnd=10708",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10643&rangeEnd=10708"
    },
    {
