      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "5282-5331",
      "markText": "假如国君能够听从我的计谋，作战必胜，我就留下来；如果不听从我的计谋，贸然用兵必然失败，我就会离去。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=838856&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5282&rangeEnd=5331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f00329505cccc8f002688c1?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5282&rangeEnd=5331"
